Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Hi, this is Sarah from Verity Capital. How are you doing today?

Speaker: Customer
Text: I'm doing well, thanks. How about you?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I'm great, thank you. I'm reaching out because I understand you're looking into some financial planning options, and I wanted to see how we might be able to assist you.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, I've been thinking about it. Planning for retirement and managing my investments have been on my mind a lot lately.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: That's completely understandable. It's crucial to have a solid plan in place. Can you tell me a little more about what you're currently doing for your financial planning?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Well, I have a 401(k) through my employer, but I feel like it's just not enough. And I'm not really sure how my other investments are performing.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Got it. Many of our clients come to us with similar concerns. Having a diversified and actively managed portfolio can make a significant difference. What's your biggest frustration right now with your current setup?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Honestly, it's the lack of clarity. I feel like I'm in the dark when it comes to how my investments are doing and whether I'm on track to meet my retirement goals.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: That's a common issue. We pride ourselves on providing transparency and clear, actionable advice. One thing we often do is an in-depth review of your current financial situation and outline a customized plan. Does that sound like something you’d be interested in?

Speaker: Customer
Text: It does, but I'm a bit worried about the costs. Financial advisors can be quite expensive.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I hear you. Budget is always a concern. At Verity Capital, we offer a range of pricing options and packages to fit different budgets. Plus, we believe that the value you'll gain from professional advice far outweighs the costs. We can go over that in detail during our consultation. Would next Tuesday at 3 PM work for you?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Tuesday at 3 PM should be fine, but I still need to think about this a bit more.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Totally understandable. Can I send you some information to review before our meeting? That way, you can get a better sense of what we offer and how we can help you reach your financial goals.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Great! I'll send over an email with some preliminary information and outline what we'll discuss in our consultation. If you have any questions before then, feel free to give me a call or send an email.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Sounds good. Thanks for reaching out.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Thank you! I look forward to speaking with you on Tuesday. Have a great day!
